Toolkit for High Energy Physics Event Generation - ThePEG

This directory contains the distribution of ThePEG as well as Pythia7,
which is implemented using ThePEG, and a directory 'test' which
contains a few test programs which are automatically run with 'make
check'.

To compile and install, run the configure script (see ThePEG/README
for details) and run 'make check' and 'make install'.

See ThePEG/README for more instructions.


